            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "財經｜小米新一代SU7今晚登場 舒淇任代言人",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜小米新一代SU7今晚登場 舒淇任代言人\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜小米新一代SU7今晚登場 舒淇任代言人</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">小米(01810)將於今晚7時舉行新一代SU7發布會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">小米表示，春季新品重磅來襲，新一代SU7即將正式上市，新一代駕駛者之車，全面升級，從容登場。同場還有兩款新品，全新小米筆記本Pro 14和小米手錶S5聯袂登場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外，小米汽車正式宣布演員舒淇成為品牌代言人，主推新一代SU7車型。小米創始人雷軍透露，兩年前第一代SU7發布時，很多網友就建議邀請舒淇代言，如今「達成大家的願望」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">內地傳媒報道，這場合作源於兩年前網友的諧音梗，即「SU7」諧音「舒淇」而建議邀請其代言。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E6%96%B0-%E4%BB%A3su7%E4%BB%8A%E6%99%9A%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4-%E8%88%92%E6%B7%87%E4%BB%BB%E4%BB%A3%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA-081846921.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-19 16:30:45",
